      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently non-operational. It requires a complete engine rebuild and has significant transmission slipping issues that prevent it from being driven. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, as it will need to be towed from its current location.",
